00:01:33.919 --> 00:01:36.760
I like to share John 14, six.

00:01:36.760 --> 00:01:38.879
It's a great verse of scripture that Jesus said,

00:01:38.879 --> 00:01:42.180
I am the way, the truth and the life.

00:01:42.180 --> 00:01:45.300
No man cometh under the father, but by me.

00:01:45.300 --> 00:01:48.199
And oftentimes I will use that verse of scripture

00:01:48.199 --> 00:01:51.519
as an introduction kind of a verse,

00:01:51.519 --> 00:01:53.019
getting right into it

00:01:53.019 --> 00:01:55.279
and being able to share with them Christ.

00:01:55.720 --> 00:01:58.000
And another verse of scripture that many people,

00:01:58.000 --> 00:02:03.000
even in our spiritually, scripturally ignorant society,

00:02:03.599 --> 00:02:05.879
John 3, 16 is a verse of scripture

00:02:05.879 --> 00:02:08.919
that I have found over the years that people,

00:02:08.919 --> 00:02:11.360
sometimes they know it, they're familiar with it,

00:02:11.360 --> 00:02:12.440
they've heard it.

00:02:12.440 --> 00:02:14.059
For God so loved the world

00:02:14.059 --> 00:02:15.720
that he gave his only begotten son,

00:02:15.720 --> 00:02:18.240
that whosoever believeth in him should not perish,

00:02:18.240 --> 00:02:19.699
but have everlasting life.

00:02:19.699 --> 00:02:22.360
And I wanna get those verses in.

00:02:22.360 --> 00:02:23.199
Why?

00:02:23.199 --> 00:02:24.759
Because God can use his word.

00:02:25.240 --> 00:02:27.479
So even if my interaction with the individual

00:02:27.479 --> 00:02:29.399
ends at that moment,

00:02:29.399 --> 00:02:32.199
there's no opportunity to be able to go any further,

00:02:32.199 --> 00:02:34.679
they're not interested, whatever it might be,

00:02:34.679 --> 00:02:37.639
I've at least had an opportunity to share

00:02:37.639 --> 00:02:40.740
some of God's word with them and God can use that.

00:02:40.740 --> 00:02:42.880
The Holy Spirit uses the word.

00:02:42.880 --> 00:02:44.919
And so what a unique opportunity.

00:02:44.919 --> 00:02:47.440
Now, let me say this, oftentimes what happens

00:02:47.440 --> 00:02:49.839
before I get into the verses of scripture,

00:02:49.839 --> 00:02:54.279
people have this idea that I need to be well-versed

00:02:54.800 --> 00:02:58.119
and trained so that no matter what the individual's

00:02:58.119 --> 00:03:02.600
religious background is, I will know what they believe

00:03:02.600 --> 00:03:06.360
