00:04:13.020 --> 00:04:18.019
but basically what he said is that Protestants,

00:04:18.420 --> 00:04:20.820
they just believe they can interpret the Bible

00:04:20.820 --> 00:04:22.820
however they want.

00:04:22.820 --> 00:04:24.380
That's not what I believe is a problem.

00:04:24.380 --> 00:04:25.859
And first of all, we're not Protestants,

00:04:25.859 --> 00:04:28.420
so I had to correct that misunderstanding.

00:04:28.420 --> 00:04:30.579
