00:04:30.579 --> 00:04:33.200
and therefore we cannot be part of the Reformation

00:04:33.200 --> 00:04:34.940
and the Protestant movement.

00:04:34.940 --> 00:04:36.420
But needless to say,

00:04:36.420 --> 00:04:38.980
I wasn't trying to have that discussion.

00:04:38.980 --> 00:04:41.059
The reality is that we don't believe

00:04:41.059 --> 00:04:43.359
that we can just interpret a passage of scripture

00:04:43.359 --> 00:04:47.119
however we want, isogete it and just come up with some,

00:04:47.160 --> 00:04:51.959
but the reality is that he had some truth

00:04:51.959 --> 00:04:54.000
that he had experienced in his life

00:04:54.000 --> 00:04:57.519
of seeing that how is it that one denomination

00:04:57.519 --> 00:04:59.279
can take a passage of scripture

00:04:59.279 --> 00:05:00.760
and interpret it a certain way,

00:05:00.760 --> 00:05:03.600
and another denomination take the same passage of scripture

00:05:03.600 --> 00:05:04.920
and interpret it a different way.

00:05:04.920 --> 00:05:06.519
And that's an experience that he's had,

00:05:06.519 --> 00:05:09.079
and so therefore he just makes this conclusion.

00:05:09.079 --> 00:05:12.040
It is far better, instead of us trying to go

00:05:12.040 --> 00:05:15.799
into the situation and take it from the approach of,

00:05:15.799 --> 00:05:18.019
oh, they say they're fill in the blank,

00:05:18.019 --> 00:05:20.600
whatever the religion is or the denomination is,

00:05:20.600 --> 00:05:23.320
and that means here's what I'm gonna begin to say,

00:05:23.320 --> 00:05:28.119
it's far better that we ask them and get information.

00:05:28.119 --> 00:05:29.320
Remember last week one of the things I said

00:05:29.320 --> 00:05:32.440
was ask questions, make inquiry.

00:05:32.440 --> 00:05:34.579
Because when you begin to ask them,

00:05:34.579 --> 00:05:38.880
then you're not just being able to make assumption

00:05:38.880 --> 00:05:40.920
based on what a denomination teaches.

00:05:40.920 --> 00:05:42.899
I have found this over the years.

00:05:42.899 --> 00:05:45.739
Most people that you come in contact with

00:05:46.579 --> 00:05:48.380
if you've done any amount of study,

00:05:48.380 --> 00:05:52.299
you know more about what their denomination believes

00:05:52.299 --> 00:05:53.140
than they do.

00:05:54.100 --> 00:05:57.200
All right, unless, there are exceptions to the rule,

00:05:57.200 --> 00:06:00.160
but rule of thumb, my experience,

00:06:00.160 --> 00:06:01.940
years and years of knocking doors

00:06:01.940 --> 00:06:03.440
and interacting with people,

00:06:03.440 --> 00:06:06.920
I know more about what they supposedly believe than they do,

00:06:06.920 --> 00:06:11.019
and the reality is that it's far more effective

00:06:11.040 --> 00:06:15.720
to have them share with you what they believe.

00:06:15.720 --> 00:06:18.720
I try to deal with the subject of going to heaven.

00:06:18.720 --> 00:06:20.559
That's what we're most concerned about.

00:06:20.559 --> 00:06:21.640
If you were to die today,

00:06:21.640 --> 00:06:24.799
are you 100% sure that heaven is your home?

00:06:24.799 --> 00:06:26.940
And that's what I'm trying to get to, why?

00:06:26.940 --> 00:06:29.920
Because death is something that all of us

00:06:29.920 --> 00:06:31.239
are going to face.

00:06:31.239 --> 00:06:33.760
And so the question is, are you 100% sure?

00:06:33.760 --> 00:06:37.040
Now, I've had repeatedly people look at me and say,

00:06:37.040 --> 00:06:40.339
well, I mean, not 100% sure,

00:06:40.359 --> 00:06:42.480
but you know, I'm fairly confident.

00:06:42.480 --> 00:06:45.320
You know, I think so, I hope so, that sort of thing.

00:06:45.320 --> 00:06:48.839
And so even if they say I'm 100% confident,

00:06:48.839 --> 00:06:51.679
here's my response, that's wonderful.

00:06:51.679 --> 00:06:53.519
Can you tell me how you know that?

00:06:55.079 --> 00:06:56.519
And then guess what I'm getting?

00:06:56.519 --> 00:06:59.239
I'm getting from them what they believe.

00:06:59.239 --> 00:07:03.640
So now I understand from them personally,

00:07:03.640 --> 00:07:06.160
not from whatever their religious background is

00:07:06.160 --> 00:07:08.399
in making some level of assumption

00:07:08.399 --> 00:07:09.619
that they must believe this,

00:07:09.619 --> 00:07:12.200
because no, they're telling me what they believe,

00:07:12.200 --> 00:07:14.279
and therefore I understand

00:07:14.279 --> 00:07:17.000
where I should focus my attention on.

00:07:17.000 --> 00:07:22.000
Most times, almost every religion of the world

00:07:22.279 --> 00:07:25.600
teaches a work-based salvation.

00:07:25.600 --> 00:07:27.720
All right, if you boil it down right there,

00:07:27.720 --> 00:07:29.160
so there's two main issues.

00:07:29.160 --> 00:07:33.200
Number one, they don't accept that Jesus Christ is God.

00:07:33.200 --> 00:07:35.440
All right, that's one issue, most of the cults.

00:07:35.440 --> 00:07:37.799
All right, the second issue is they believe

00:07:37.820 --> 00:07:41.739
