00:08:20.480 --> 00:08:23.600
when I die, I probably would have said, I hope so.

00:08:23.600 --> 00:08:26.359
I think I had a pretty basic understanding

00:08:26.359 --> 00:08:27.679
that there's heaven and hell,

00:08:27.679 --> 00:08:31.720
and I didn't know a whole lot about anything more than that,

00:08:31.720 --> 00:08:33.520
but I think I would have said, I hope so.

00:08:33.520 --> 00:08:35.039
And if you asked me how I would have known,

00:08:35.039 --> 00:08:38.900
I had in my mind this idea of really this big scale,

00:08:38.900 --> 00:08:40.659
